* Declare variable

  In Lua, we usually use 'local' to declare variables.

  .image pic/123/3.png

  You can also declare variables without using 'local', then this variable is global.

  .image pic/123/4.png

  In Lua, it is advisable to avoid declaring global variables as much as possible, especially in Redis.


